{"_path":"/city/t003","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"大專校院學生校內住宿補貼計畫","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t003-1.jpeg","sequence":3,"category":"教育補助","author":"教育科學文化處","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2023-11-23T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"大專校院學生校內住宿補貼計畫"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ey.gov.tw/Page/448DE008087A1971/b9445765-ae86-40fb-b47b-749cb682e32c?fbclid=IwAR1xNFFzOO3tEVGsY3cNhTb211QKTazt5CTMQCNaXtfmywWfKtpWM5fSu0Y"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大專校院學生校內住宿補貼計畫"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一、推動理念：教育部為減輕學生校內住宿負擔，支持青年專心就學，考量目前「弱勢學生校外住宿租金補貼」額度、校內外住宿的價差，以及配合學校採學期制收取宿舍費等，規劃補貼大專校院學生校內住宿費用，預計自 113 年 2 月起實施。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二、補貼原則："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"(一)「一般身分」住宿生：每名每學期以補貼 5,000 元為原則；如學校住宿費用低於 5,000 元者，補貼至與其住宿費用相同。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"(二)「經濟弱勢身分」住宿生：針對低收入戶、中低收入戶身分者每名每學期以補貼 7,000 元為原則；如學校住宿費用低於 7,000 元者，補貼至與其住宿費用相同。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三、預期效益：本案預計協助約 27. 5 萬名校內住宿學生(含經濟弱勢學生約 1 萬名)減輕住宿負擔。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t003-1.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t003-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"大專校院學生校內住宿補貼計畫","depth":2,"text":"大專校院學生校內住宿補貼計畫"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t003.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t003.md","_extension":"md"}